long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Super Liquid Soccer Unblocked is a dynamic soccer game with many teams and nice 3D graphics. This game stands out with its unique, liquid-like animation style that adds an extra layer of fun and challenge to the traditional soccer gameplay. You have lots of different ways to play from chip passes to through balls so find your play style and see if you can become World Champion! You can also play penalties so get your boots on and get ready to take and save some! Can you handle the pressure and become a world champion?

How to play?
Movement: WASD
Pass: M
Shoot: J
Chip: L
Through pass: I
Switch player: Q or E
Sprint: P or O
